# iCloud account for colinstein@me.com
IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
AuthMechs LOGIN
User colinstein
Pass IOUONEPASSWORD
# PassCmd "echo 'pull this from keychain'"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/cert.pem

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
Path ~/.mail/icloud/
Inbox ~/.mail/icloud/Inbox

Channel icloud
Master :icloud-remote:
Slave :icloud-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
